<h3 class="review_header">



<a href="/dist/SQL-Statement">


SQL-Statement</a>

   (<a href="https://metacpan.org/release/SQL-Statement/">1.405</a>)




<img src="//cdn.perl.org/perlweb/cpanratings/images/stars-3.0.png" alt="***">

</h3>



<blockquote class="review_text">
The concept is truly cool, unfortunately the parser is currently flaky/buggy: one SQL query might work but another valid and seemingly simple SQL would fail with weird error message. See distribution's RT queue.<br>

</blockquote>


