My favorite 2048 implementation (it's text-mode, written in Perl, uses my module Color::ANSI::Util, and what else... oh yeah, it's the only implementation where I've reached 2048 :-) ).<br><br>One tip: enlarge the fonts of your terminal emulator (e.g. Ctrl-+ on Konsole) until it's big and convenient enough.
</blockquote>


