<div class="review" data-review="11818" data-user="10616">
<a name="11818"></a>
<h3 class="review_header">



<a href="/dist/Hash-Ordered">


Hash-Ordered</a>

   (<a href="https://metacpan.org/release/Hash-Ordered/">0.002</a>)



</h3>



<blockquote class="review_text">
Overall looks ok, with the exception that it does not look and feel like a regular Perl hash at all. Now someone just needs to create a tie interface on top of this :)<br>

</blockquote>


