</h3>



<blockquote class="review_text">
Why exclude Moo?<br><br>Also the issue with any Any::* (or Any::*) modules is that there should be a mechanism (preferably a common one) to adjust the ordering. Sometimes I prefer Moose first, for full capability or compatibility or whatever. Sometimes I prefer Mouse or Moo, for quick startup (but don't mind Moose if those are not available). This also happens to me for YAML::Any: in some cases I prefer YAML::Syck, in others YAML::XS, this depends on the data that I'm handling.<br>

</blockquote>


